00:17:29,559 --> 00:17:31,160
<font color="#FFFFFF">You all work 'em out.</font>

383
00:17:31,190 --> 00:17:32,930
<font color="#FFFFFF">Leave me alone.</font>

384
00:17:32,960 --> 00:17:34,630
<font color="#FFFFFF">You're stuck in another time,</font>

385
00:17:34,660 --> 00:17:38,569
<font color="#FFFFFF">afraid to change no matter how
