393
00:17:53,279 --> 00:17:57,690
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's a load-bearing wall!</font>

394
00:17:57,720 --> 00:18:00,190
<font color="#FFFFFF">Oh, God, Darryl, I...</font>

395
00:18:00,220 --> 00:18:02,660
<font color="#FFFFFF">I tried, years ago.</font>

396
00:18:02,690 --> 00:18:04,230
<font color="#FFFFFF">But before the remodel,
